proof:
Proof using.
    unfold issuable, E.
    case_eq (I ∩₁ tc_coherent T); [intros Y P; unfold same_trav_config in P|].
    apply in_issuable, in_coherent; [unfold same_trav_config; desf; auto| ].
    apply traversal_mon.
    + intros E E' QE. apply in_issuable. apply TCCOH.
    intros H H'. apply in_issuable. apply TCCOH. by unfold issuable. 
    unfold issuable; desf. by apply traversal_mon. apply IMMCON.
    + apply in_issuable. by eapply traversal_mon. by apply issuable_in.
      by unfold issuable, TCCOH in H'.
      by apply in_issuable. by apply isu_issue_in.
      eapply traversal_mon. by apply issuable_covers.
      unfold covered. by apply (@eq_subset actid_covers (I (I (is_init x)))).
      by apply (@eq_subset (X ∩ T) (X ∩ same_tid)).
      by apply (@eq_subset ∪ (I (I same_tid))) in TCCOH.
    + by unfold issuable in H'. 2,3: tc_invert.
      + by unfold issuable in H'; auto.
      + by apply issuable_in.
        * by apply isu_in_same_loc.
        * by apply TCCOH. eapply issuable_more; by eassumption. eauto.
        * by unfold same_trav_config, traits, traversal_trav_config; unfold traversal_path_t.
          exists (_,_); apply ppo_same_id. simpl; unfold dom_rel. exists H; simpl; auto.
          apply traversal_inc.
          apply isu_issue_move.
          by apply traversal_mon. red; simpl; auto.
          exists H; auto.
          split.
            apply in_issuable. apply isu_issue_in. apply TCCOH. apply TCCOH.
            apply in_issuable. apply tc_correct with H; auto.
            apply in_issuable in H'. apply TCCOH in H'. apply isu_issue_in in H'. by rewrite H'.  
            by unfold issuable in H'.
            eapply traversal_mon. eapply traversal_mon_path.
            eapply traversal_t_mon_path; eauto.
            by apply isu_correct. eapply traversal_mon.
            by eapply TCCOH.
            eapply issuable_more.
            unfold issuable; auto.
            by apply traversal_mon.
            apply traversal_ir. red.
            by exists H.
          2: apply traversal_inc; simp; auto.
          exists H; simpl; auto.
          split; [| by apply in_issuable; apply in_issuable in H']; auto.
          split; auto.
          2: apply traversal_inc; auto.
          by apply isu_in in H'.
          2: apply traversal_inc; auto.
          4: by apply isu_in; auto.
          4: by apply traversal_ir_principle; auto.
            eapply isu_more_ir_same_tid; by apply TCCOH.
            by apply issuable_in. apply @in_issuable. apply in_issuable.
      unfold act_in_set. eapply traversal_ir_same_tid.
      { apply tc_correct with H; auto.
        eapply traversal_imply_same_tid.
        by apply WF.
        by apply IMMCON; auto.
        apply equi_sym. exact @in_wf.
        apply in_issuable; auto.
        apply in_wf. by apply IMMCON.
        unfold issuable; auto. by apply in_wf.
        apply issuable_in. exists H; red; simpl; auto.
         by exists {H; red; simpl; auto}. exists H; simpl; auto.
          by apply in_wf. apply in_wf. by exists H.
          by exists H; red; simpl; auto.
      }
      { apply well_founded. apply TCCOH. exists H; red; simpl; auto.
        by apply ar_rf_ppo_loc_ct_in_ar_ct. 
        red. apply isu_in. apply in_issuable in H'. constructor 1; auto.
        apply in_issuable in H'. constructor 2; auto.
        by apply ppo_in_sb; auto.
        apply traversal_ir_principle; auto.
        by eapply TCCOH; exists H; red; simpl; auto.
        apply traversal_imp_same_tid with same_tid; auto. exists H; red; simpl; auto.
        by red. by exists H.
      }
      apply in_issuable in H'. exists 1. 
      by constructor 1; exists H; auto.
      by constructor 2; exists H; auto.
      apply equi_refl. red; constructor; auto.
Qed.
